    {
      "type": "TEXT",
      "value": "<ul><li>On 2024-06-05: days_from_last_change(x) = 2</li><li>On 2024-06-06: days_from_last_change(x) = 0</li></ul><p><b>Examples</b></p><p>Last_earnings_date = days_from_last_change(ern2_earnrelease_d1_calendar_prev);</p><p>alpha = rank(operating_income/cap);</p><p>trade_when(Last_earnings_date == 0, alpha, -1)</p>",
